data.description: You can move into this spacious home in 45 days. Home features a living room, a large family and dining room. Family room can be easily converted into a fifth bedroom on the first floor with four additional bedrooms on the second floor. Each bedroom large enough to hold a king size bed wit lots of closet space. 1.5 bath and laundry room. Hardwood floors throughout. Two large garages space with additional space for storage. Could be easily converted into a central air. Need some updating. A MUST SEE.
